		<h1 class="post-title"><a href="http://thepioneerwoman.com/cooking/2012/03/my-last-breakfast-in-colorado/" title="My Last Breakfast in Colorado">My Last Breakfast in Colorado</a></h1>
		<p class="posted-by">
								<span class="alignright">
						<a href="http://thepioneerwoman.com/cooking/2012/03/my-last-breakfast-in-colorado/#commentform" class="comment-number">142 Comments</a>
											</span>
						Posted by Ree in <a href="http://thepioneerwoman.com/cooking/category/miscellaneous/eating-out/" title="View all posts in Eating Out" rel="category tag">Eating Out</a></p>
		<div class="clr"></div>
		<div class="post-padding">
						<div class="category-big category-thumb-border">
