		<h1 class="post-title"><a href="http://thepioneerwoman.com/cooking/2012/02/my-second-meal-in-colorado/" title="My Second Meal in Colorado">My Second Meal in Colorado</a></h1>
		<p class="posted-by">
								<span class="alignright">
						<a href="http://thepioneerwoman.com/cooking/2012/02/my-second-meal-in-colorado/#commentform" class="comment-number">122 Comments</a>
											</span>
						Posted by Ree in <a href="http://thepioneerwoman.com/cooking/category/miscellaneous/eating-out/" title="View all posts in Eating Out" rel="category tag">Eating Out</a></p>
		<div class="clr"></div>
		<div class="post-padding">
						<div class="category-big category-thumb-border">
					<img width="213" height="142" src="http://static.thepioneerwoman.com/cooking/files/2012/02/quail-213x142.jpg" class="category-big wp-post-image" alt="quail" title="quail" />					<img src="http://static.thepioneerwoman.com/wp-content/themes/multi/images/category-thumb-bottom.gif" class="category-thumb-bottom"/>
				</div>
				<div class='excerpt'><p>As I chronicle the meals I eat while in Vail, keep in mind that I&#8217;m focusing on complete restaurant meals and not quick snacks or salads or Ding Dongs here and there. &nbsp; Last night, all twelve of us headed to this spot in Lionshead Village. Anything with the words &#8220;chop house&#8221; in the name always sounds promising to us cattle rancher types. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Of course, I had to immediately check out the&hellip;<a class="more-link" href="http://thepioneerwoman.com/cooking/2012/02/my-second-meal-in-colorado/" title="Continue reading My Second Meal in Colorado" class="keep-reading">Keep Reading &rarr;</a></p></div><div class="clr"></div>		</div>
		<div class="meta">
			<p class="tagged">
				<span class="share"><a href="#" class="sprite mail-icon" target="_blank">Email This</a><a href="http://twitter.com/home?status=My+Second+Meal+in+Colorado+http%3A%2F%2Fthepioneerwoman.com%2Fcooking%2F%3Fp%3D11533" class="sprite twitter-icon" target="_blank">Twitter</a><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthepioneerwoman.com%2Fcooking%2F2012%2F02%2Fmy-second-meal-in-colorado%2F&t=My+Second+Meal+in+Colorado" class="facebook-icon sprite" target="_blank">Facebook</a>Share: </span><span>|</span><span class="sprite com-num"><a href="http://thepioneerwoman.com/cooking/2012/02/my-second-meal-in-colorado/#comments">122 Comments</a></span>
